"ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 1, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1012726, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 3, "EnglishDescription": "The ancestor of the Holy Prophet (s), Abd Munaf, grandfather Abdul Muttalib, uncle Abu Talib, wife Khadijah (s), other great scholars and believers are buried in this graveyard.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Isi qabrastaan mein Paighambar (s) ke jade aala Hazrat Abd’e Munaaf, Aap (s) ke jadd Hazrat Abdul Muttalib (a), Aap (s) ke chacha Hazrat Abu Taalib (a), Aap (s) ki zauja’e giraami Janabe Khadija (s) ke alaawa baaz ulma’e allaam aur bohot se momeneen ki qabre’n hai.", "UrduDescription": "اسی قبرستان میں پیغمبرؐ کے جد اعلی حضرت عبد مناف، آپؐ کے جد حضرت عبد المطلبؑ، آپؐ کے چچا حضرت ابو طالبؑ، آپؐ کی زوجۂ گرامی جناب خدیجہؑ کے علاوہ بعض علماء اعلام اور بہت سے مومنین کی قبریں ہیں۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicTex